        <img alt="Sign in to WWT" src="@Model.ImgDir/news/sign-in-to-wwt.jpg" class="img-responsive img-border" />
    </li>
    <li>
        When you are logged in click again on your profile button, which should now be blue. This will show you a list of your <strong>Uploads</strong>, <strong>Communities</strong> and <strong>Requests</strong> [to join a community you manage].<br />
        <img alt="Sign in to WWT" src="@Model.ImgDir/news/logged-into-wwt.jpg" class="img-responsive" />
    </li>
    <li>You can either navigate to a community you have previously setup or you can create a new community for your submission here. Navigate to that community.&nbsp; And click the blue &ldquo;Add Content&rdquo; button.&nbsp; Navigate to your Tour and click the blue &ldquo;Publish&rdquo; button in the lower right.</li>
    <li>
